</strong> Verified opening extract and source note for Kanda Sashti Kavasam.</p><p>Only the verified opening extract is published in this release. A complete critical edition remains outside Release 147.</p></article></section><section class="card" style="margin-top:22px"><h2>Publication states</h2><ul><li><strong>Published — source linked:</strong> primary-text citation is visible on the page.</li><li><strong>Partial reviewed:</strong> only the identified extract is published; completeness is not claimed.</li><li><strong>Directory review:</strong> basic navigation entry remains available but is excluded from search indexing, sitemap publication and the offline precache.</li></ul><h2>Claims deliberately deferred</h2><p>Release 147 does not claim inscription dates, architectural chronology, daily temple timings, annual festival dates or a complete critical edition of any long devotional work unless a suitable authoritative source is available.</p><p><a class="btn" href="literature/thirumurugatruppadai.html">Read the Thirumurugatruppadai cross-reference</a></p></section></main><footer>© Om Saravana Bhava · Static GitHub Pages safe platform · <a href="sources.html">Sources &amp; publication policy</a></footer></body></html>--- baseline/temples.html
